程序包 projecttwo

Enum Class Location

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<Location>
projecttwo.Location
所有已实现的接口:
Serializable, Comparable<Location>, Constable
public enum Location extends Enum<Location>
This enum is for the creation and retrieving of a Location enum constant. Each location has a zipcode and also a county that can be retrieved, and also compared
作者:
Kangwei Zhu, Michael Israel

    • compareLocation

      public int compareLocation(Member member)
      This compareLocation Method compares the Locations of two members. Checks and compares county's and if equal returns difference of their zipcodes
      参数:
      member - the object to be compared.
      返回:
      a number smaller than 0 if first county smaller than second or equal but firstZipCode smaller than secondZipCode, 0 if two locations are equal, a number greater than 0 if first county greater than second or equal but firstZipCode > secondZipCode
